                  | Project Name
  aside.bg-dark
    .container.text-center
      .call-to-action
        h2 Discord Voice / Chat Client
        a.btn.btn-default.btn-xl.wow.tada(href='https://discordapp.com/download') Download Now!
  section#contact
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2.text-center
          h2.section-heading Contact Info
          hr.primary
          p
            | Ready to purchase 8/8 Gold? That's great! We prefer you contact us using Discord but we are also available via E-Mail
          p
            | Please Provide Your Battletag, Faction, and Server
          hr.primary
        .col-lg-4.col-lg-offset-2.text-center
          p
            a(href="https://discord.gg/0jAxkRz9u7fhqGmL") Discord Sales Server
        .col-lg-4.text-center
          p
            a(href='mailto:SoulKappaIndustries@gmail.com') SoulKappaIndustries@gmail.com
